data.description:
LOCATED ON A CUL-DE-SAC IN WINDMILL FARMS, THIS 2-STORY 3BR/2.5BA HOME BOASTS 2,205 SQ.FT. W/ 2 LVNG AREAS, & A SOFT, NEUTRAL COLOR PALETTE THROUGHOUT. THE 1ST FLOOR OFFERS AN OPEN-CONCEPT PLAN W/ A WOOD TILE LIV RM, & ADJACENT KIT & DIN AREA W/ TILED FLOORS & BACK PATIO ACCESS. GRANITE COUNTERS, STAINED CABINETRY, STAINLESS APPLIANCES, BAR SEATING, & WALK-IN PANTRY COMPLETE THE KITCHEN. ALSO LOCATED DOWNSTAIRS IS A 1/2 BATH & UTILITY RM. AT THE TOP OF THE STAIRS, UNIQUE BARN DOORS PROVIDE PRIVACY FOR THE 2ND FLOOR, W/ 2 SPARE BED RMS & A BATH RM. A 2ND LVNG AREA IS ALSO AVAILABLE FOR MEDIA SPACE/OFFICE USE. RETREAT TO THE SPACIOUS
MASTER SUITE & ENJOY A MASTER BATH W/ DOUBLE VANITY, SEPARATE TUB & SHOWER, & WALK-IN CLOSET. OUTDOOR LIVING AWAITS IN THE FENCED BACKYARD WHILE RELAXING UNDER THE PERGOLA, OR GRILLING IN THE OUTDOOR KITCHEN AREA.
